<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Question Reply Notification</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        background-color: #e9ecef;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff, #f7f9fc);
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border: 1px solid #dde2e6;
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        padding-bottom: 20px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .header h1 {
        font-size: 26px;
        color: #007acc;
        margin: 0;
      }
      h2 {
        font-size: 22px;
        color: #333;
      }
      p {
        margin: 0 0 10px;
        color: #555;
      }
      blockquote {
        margin: 10px 0;
        padding: 15px;
        background-color: #f1f3f5;
        border-left: 4px solid #007acc;
        font-style: italic;
        color: #333;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        margin-top: 15px;
        background-color: #007acc;
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .button:hover {
        background-color: #005a9e;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #888;
        text-align: center;
        border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
        padding-top: 10px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Question Reply Notification</h1>
      </div>
      <p>Hello <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>
      <p>
        A new reply has been added to your question in the video titled "<strong
          >Introduction to Programming</strong
        >": "<%= title %>"
      </p>
      <p>Reply:</p>
      <blockquote>
        Thank you for your question. Here is the detailed answer to your query.
      </blockquote>
      <p>If you have any further questions, feel free to ask.</p>
      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <p><strong>Your Learning Management Team</strong></p>
      <a href="#" class="button">View Your Question</a>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Learning Management System. All
          rights reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
